               <msContents>
                  <summary>An incomplete copy of the autobiography of the poet <persName key="person_50013027" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/50013027/" role="aut subject" change="#role-assignment">ʻAlī Ḥazīn‏</persName>.</summary>
